pa_ppx_regexp Version 8.04.01
-----------------------------

* [09 May 2026] 

  * update source to be compat with pa_ppx 8.04.01

    specifically, `pa_ppx.import` changed the behaviour of "@with"
    [check pa_ppx/CHANGES] and this affected code here.

  * Change version-numbering of pa_ppx so it matches that of Camlp5, since
    it is almost always the case that a new version of Camlp5 requires a
    new version of pa_ppx's base infra, and when it's new syntax, changes
    to the various derivers to support that new syntax.

  * sync config/Makefile*

